Spread rumors that Shima-kun

395
00:31:30,927 --> 00:31:32,440
was seducing him first,

396
00:31:32,950 --> 00:31:34,230
blamed all his work mistakes

397
00:31:34,243 --> 00:31:35,283
on Shima-kun,

398
00:31:35,730 --> 00:31:37,590
