399
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:43,190
Apparently they were dating, though.

400
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:47,730
So what?

401
00:31:49,010 --> 00:31:52,200
- Am I supposed to do something?
- No. It's just...

402
00:31:52,820 --> 00:31:54,200
I saw that you took good care

403
00:31:54,207 --> 00:31:55,327
of Shima-kun.

404
00:31:57,910 --> 00:32:00,107
Well, we've worked together

405
00:32:00,148 --> 00:32:01,581
for a while so you can tell.

406
00:32:15,300 --> 00:32:16,130
Then...

407
00:32:17,600 --> 00:32:18,840
I'll head out for the day.

408
00:32:19,360 --> 00:32:20,840
- Thanks for your hard work.
- Thanks for your hard work.

409
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:21,840
Thanks for your hard work.

410
00:32:55,780 --> 00:32:56,905
How long have you even

411
00:32:56,930 --> 00:32:58,096
been doing this job?

412
00:32:58,842 --> 00:32:59,955
Maybe he's too distracted

413
00:32:59,976 --> 00:33:01,409
thinking about something else?

414
00:33:04,160 --> 00:33:05,330
Sorry about earlier.

415
00:33:07,380 --> 00:33:09,030
Please don't be angry with me.

416
00:33:10,770 --> 00:33:11,880
Shima!

417
00:33:58,420 --> 00:33:59,200
Yes?

418
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:01,840
Hello, it's me.

419
00:34:05,280 --> 00:34:06,230
What is it?

420
00:34:07,590 --> 00:34:08,740
