421
00:34:12,850 --> 00:34:13,760
Watching TV.

422
00:34:14,690 --> 00:34:16,900
I see, rubbing one out, huh?

423
00:34:17,190 --> 00:34:18,320
I am not.

424
00:34:19,990 --> 00:34:20,880
