425
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,750
Mmm...

426
00:34:30,450 --> 00:34:31,830
Say something, will ya?

427
00:34:32,980 --> 00:34:34,300
You're the one who called me,

428
00:34:34,325 --> 00:34:35,325
