429
00:34:37,620 --> 00:34:38,600
Right.

430
00:34:46,160 --> 00:34:47,030
You see...

431
00:34:48,950 --> 00:34:51,590
- About yesterday...
- Come pick me up.

432
00:34:53,170 --> 00:34:53,880
Huh?

433
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:56,150
I'm at the station near your place.

434
00:34:59,560 --> 00:35:00,310
Why?

435
00:35:01,693 --> 00:35:03,393
