440
00:35:15,830 --> 00:35:16,950
What even is that?

441
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:18,980
Say goodbye to your bonus,

442
00:35:19,890 --> 00:35:21,116
Could be like

443
00:35:21,143 --> 00:35:22,436
100,000 yen down the drain.

444
00:35:24,310 --> 00:35:25,510
