447
00:35:47,350 --> 00:35:48,630
Please take care of it,

448
00:35:49,490 --> 00:35:50,480
Section Chief Togawa.

449
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:55,640
I said it might drop,

450
00:35:55,665 --> 00:35:57,173
didn't say it could go up.

451
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:00,738
You don't actually have

452
00:36:00,759 --> 00:36:01,972
that much power, do you?

453
00:36:04,130 --> 00:36:05,170
Shut it.

454
00:36:24,040 --> 00:36:24,980
Make some room.

455
00:36:27,040 --> 00:36:28,500
It's a single bed,

456
00:36:28,953 --> 00:36:30,290
