469
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:35,570
It's related to

470
00:37:36,040 --> 00:37:37,560
the reason why you quit your old job.

471
00:37:44,290 --> 00:37:45,970
Onoda knows someone

472
00:37:46,980 --> 00:37:49,490
at your previous company.

473
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:58,443
You don't have to talk about it

474
00:37:58,463 --> 00:37:59,489
if you don't want to.

475
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:12,690
I hate that I'm into guys.

476
00:38:19,410 --> 00:38:20,920
I wish I'd never met you.

477
00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:29,200
Huh?

478
00:38:30,360 --> 00:38:31,650
- Good morning.
- Yes.

479
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:32,760
Good morning.

480
00:38:34,040 --> 00:38:35,730
Togawa-san, late again?

481
00:38:36,420 --> 00:38:38,610
