486
00:38:58,530 --> 00:39:01,080
Shima-kun, it's all over your face.

487
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:04,678
Since you're usually so unreadable,

488
00:39:04,698 --> 00:39:05,718
it's extra obvious.

489
00:39:10,800 --> 00:39:13,269
I mean, I didn't think you two

490
00:39:13,289 --> 00:39:14,969
