491
00:39:15,540 --> 00:39:16,580
We're not together.

492
00:39:18,130 --> 00:39:19,250
Huh? Really?

493
00:39:21,590 --> 00:39:23,000
We're not dating or anything.

494
00:39:27,380 --> 00:39:28,630
- So...
- Oh. It's okay.

495
00:39:30,260 --> 00:39:31,840
What did Shima say?

496
00:39:32,530 --> 00:39:33,880
He didn't deny it.

497
00:39:36,070 --> 00:39:37,040
Huh...

498
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:39,750
But he said you're not together.

499
00:39:40,500 --> 00:39:41,250
And?

500
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:44,380
Man, this feels like tattling,

501
00:39:44,407 --> 00:39:45,436
I don't like it.

502
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:47,120
I'll bump up your bonus.

503
