508
00:40:03,490 --> 00:40:04,820
But he's not.

509
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:07,030
It's just...

510
00:40:08,930 --> 00:40:09,970
He probably sees me

511
00:40:09,990 --> 00:40:10,990
