564
00:43:13,330 --> 00:43:14,130
Well...

565
00:43:15,170 --> 00:43:17,120
- It's weird.
- How so?

566
00:43:18,710 --> 00:43:20,260
Like, being strangely kind suddenly,

567
00:43:20,710 --> 00:43:21,860
or quitting smoking.

568
00:43:22,470 --> 00:43:23,250
Huh?

569
00:43:23,816 --> 00:43:25,886
I've always been kind.

570
00:43:32,070 --> 00:43:33,830
I'll make dinner today,

571
00:43:34,530 --> 00:43:35,760
